data.description: Seize the moment with this exceptional multi-unit property located in the Austin Neighborhood, tailor-made for the seasoned investor or savvy handyman in search of a robust cash flow generator. This is your canvas, and the potential is boundless. Presenting two side-by-side two-story units, Each offers expansive attics and full basements, providing a wealth of space to craft your vision.    In the rear, a coach house awaits, boasting three bedrooms and a well-appointed bath, complete with its own full basement, a touch of TLC could breathe new life into its character.    Being sold AS-IS, this property is a blank canvas awaiting your personal touch. Embrace the freedom to reimagine floor plans, creating spaces that resonate with your vision.
